# Root URL of the deployed Storybook. Used for the header "Storybook" button,
# the docs "Open Storybook" link, and every component's "View on Storybook"
# deep link. When unset, the demo falls back to `/storybook/` served next to
# itself (the CI/GitHub Pages layout).
# VITE_STORYBOOK_HOST=https://storybook.honami.dev
